---
title: Creamy Mushroom Lovers' Ravioli with Toasted Walnuts
description: Mushroom lovers, rejoice! We're doubling down on mushrooms tonight. Mushroom ravioli is tossed with more mushrooms in a creamy white wine sauce, then topped with walnuts for a luxurious veggie-forward dinner!
